Seriously simplified.</span>[/hanor_video_popup][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1538211354689{padding-top: 6% !important;}"][vc_column][havnor_section_title title_align="center" title_text="Popular Questions" content_text="Find a short list of our most frequently asked questions." btm_space="5%" title_size="36px" title_btm="0px"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1536319502932{padding-bottom: 8% !important;}"][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6"][vc_accordion accordion_style="style-one"][vc_accordion_tab title="How does security system communicate?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Our systems use dual-path technology (cellular and Wi-Fi) to connect your security panel to the Alarm Response Center, as well as your mobile app. During an alarm, the system automatically selects the fastest way to connect. It's more responsive, more connected, and more secure.

Your home sensors communicate with the panel using encrypted low-power radio signals that don't require your Wi-Fi network.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Will my security work if my wireless network goes?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Yes. Your system has 4G LTE cellular backup to make sure your home is still professionally monitored.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Are wireless security systems secure?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Absolutely. It's much easier for an intruder to cut a landline than disrupt the wireless signal to the Alarm Response Center. If an intruder tries to break your security panel or base, it will set off an alarm before the system is compromised.

Wireless sensors are also secure. Since they aren't constrained by phone lines or wall mounts, they can be placed out of view of intruders. If a sensor is tampered with, an alarm will be triggered as well.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Can I turn the alarm system on and off?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Yes. You can use a passcode to arm and disarm it from the panel. You can also use the mobile app or a keychain remote.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="My system connected to home automation devices?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]That's a popular option for many Brinks Home Security customers. Your system can serve as a hub for up to 119 Z-wave smart sensors and devices, such as video cameras, locks and lights. Compatible devices from multiple manufacturers can be controlled remotely from the mobile app.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Do pets trigger motion sensors?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]In general, only pets over 40 lbs. are capable of triggering motion sensors. To safeguard against pet-triggered alarms, we suggest following the recommendations provided with your security system, and (if possible) setting motion detectors in areas that pets don't normally frequent.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Why don't your systems include window sensors?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Our door sensors can also be used as window sensors, though window sensors aren't cost-effective for home protection. Window break-ins are rare, and with the effective protection provided by well-placed door and motion sensors, window sensors are rarely necessary. If you absolutely need window sensors, just add extra door sensors when you purchase your system.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6"][vc_accordion accordion_style="style-one"][vc_accordion_tab title="When a security breach occurs?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Yes. Each sensor protects a door, window, or area, and will indicate the location of the breach when an alarm occurs.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Without good cellular service will system work?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Absolutely. Your system uses dual-path connectivity to communicate over the best signal—whether it's Wi-Fi or cellular. The cellular service will come from either AT&amp;T or Verizon, depending on which carrier is stronger at your home. Just call or chat us to let us know if you have a preference.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Does my security system have a warranty?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Your system hardware is covered by a 2-year limited warranty. If anything breaks during the first two years, we'll replace it[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Take my system with me if I move to new home?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Yes. That's one of the advantages of a wireless self-installed system. Just take the devices down from your old home and place them in your new home. Once you have installed your system in the new location, just call or chat to let us know. Your monthly rate will remain the same unless you choose to add additional services.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Can I get an additional system for my home?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Of course! Just call or chat with one of our security experts to get started.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What is professional monitoring?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]A professionally monitored system transmits alarm signals to an Alarm Response Center, a sophisticated 24/7 call center that can rapidly notify police, fire or medical authorities during any emergency.

Around-the-clock professional monitoring is especially important because calling 911 on your cell phone won't connect you to the correct authorities unless you're currently located within their jurisdiction. The professionals in our monitoring center will alert the correct authorities no matter where you are.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="How many months is the monitoring agreement?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Your agreement is for 36 months. We'll do everything we can to make sure you're happy with your new system, but you can cancel at any time in the first 30 days with no termination fee.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1542609687854{padding-top: 4% !important;padding-bottom: 4% !important;background-color: #1429a0 !important;}"][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1538211680142{padding-top: 0px !important;}"][havnor_callout call_style="three" call_title="JOIN WITH 24/7 SECURED TECHNICAL EXPERTISE PROVIDER" btn_text="Connect Now" btn_link="#0" open_link="true" btn_text_color="#ffffff" btn_text_hover_color="#87c818" btn_bg_color="#87c818" btn_bg_hover_color="#ffffff" btn_border_color="#87c818" btn_border_hover_color="#ffffff" cta_bg_color="#1429a0" title_size="24px"][/havnor_callout][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1538211920668{padding-top: 3% !important;}"][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1544504237003{padding-bottom: 30px !important;}" offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6"][havnor_section_title title_align="left" title_text="Protect &amp; Manage What Matters Most Security" btm_space="20px" title_btm="0px"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1539259301497{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-right: 10% !important;}"]We are deeply dedicated to the long-term growth and success of our clients and our people. We are dedicated to producing measured value and results.[/vc_column_text][havnor_button button_align="left" button_text="Watch Now" button_link="#0" open_link="" text_color="#ffffff" bgg_color="#87c818" border_color="#87c818" text_hover_color="#87c818" bg_hover_color="#ffffff" border_hover_color="#87c818"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/12" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][/vc_column][vc_column text_alignment="text-center" offset="vc_col-lg-5 vc_col-md-5"][vc_single_image img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1544504726086{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row]
